snippet.title: 🤖🤣 Funny Robot Mobile Game
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching ♥ http://JenniNexus.com ~~ Excited to share “9 to 5 Smash It” - the 1st mobile game produced by developer RasCom Games.  It’s made with Unity, my favorite game dev software, by one of my good friends, so I *am* biased!  But also, I genuinely think the game has unique mechanics, a witty sense of humor, cute robots made by my friend, and a really awesome soundtrack, produced by synthwave musician Protector 101.  I play a LOT of mobile games, but don’t often find ones that really reel in my attention, but this one did.  I paid $1.99 for it & it’s refreshing to enjoy a fun mobile game without any ads.

★ Featured in this video: “9 to 5 Smash It” in the Google Play store ►► https://goo.gl/YPacAs 
► https://facebook.com/RasComGames
► https://twitter.com/RasComVR (same dev also works in VR!)
► Game Soundtrack https://protector101.bandcamp.com
► Intro / outro music: Thanks to the musician & free Youtube audio library for use of “Dragonfly” by Quincas Moreira

★ My Channels 🎥
╔► Main Channel: http://youtube.com/JenniNexus 
╠► ✂️ DIY Fashion Channel: http://youtube.com/DIYwithJenni
╚► 🎮 Gaming Channel: http://youtube.com/c/JenniNexusPlaysGames



 

.
#Unity3d #mobilegame #madewithunity
